\
Here's what you just learned: [CHAPTER POINT].\
\
This isn't about fixing \{book_topic\}. It's about [deeper meaning].
\f0 \
\
#### **Option B: Pause + Repeat Pattern (Phoenix Protocol Style)**\
Use your existing pause system to create emphasis:\
\

