\
This is the skill you're building today.
\f0 \
\
#### **Option C: Weave It Through Integration (Distributed Encoding)**\
Instead of 3\'d7 at the start, weave it into:\
1. **Post-exercise integration** ("You just practiced [point]...")\
2. **Aspirational story** (someone using this skill)\
3. **Carry sentence** (take-away that echoes the point)\
\
