## **Why "Observer Lens" Is The RIGHT Name**\
\
### **1. Describes Function, Not Grammar**\
\
**"First-Person"** = grammatical term (I/me/my pronouns)\
- Tells you HOW it's written\
- Doesn't tell you WHAT it does\
- Creates memoir expectation\
\
**"Observer Lens"** = functional term (viewing patterns through "I")\
- Tells you WHAT it does\
- Describes the mechanism\
- Creates observation expectation\
