## Architecture Overview\
\
### Current State\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f7 \cf0 Chapter structure:\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  Validation ("You know what it's like...")\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  Embodiment (physical sensations)\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  Tension Peak (daily struggles)\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  \{EXERCISE_SLOT\}\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  Brief integration ("You just mapped your body...")  \u8592  Too quick\
\uc0\u9492 \u9472  Stories + Close\
\
Problem: Chapter point stated once, quickly, then moved on.
\f0 \
\
### Target State\
\

\f7 Enhanced chapter structure:\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  Validation\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  SEED (implicit recognition)  \u8592  NEW\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  Embodiment + Tension Peak\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  \{EXERCISE_SLOT\}\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  NAME (explicit integration)  \u8592  ENHANCED\
\uc0\u9474    \u9500 \u9472  Core statement\
\uc0\u9474    \u9500 \u9472  What it's NOT\
\uc0\u9474    \u9500 \u9472  Practical application\
\uc0\u9474    \u9492 \u9472  Mechanism reinforcement\
\uc0\u9500 \u9472  Recognition story (reinforces point)  \u8592  ENHANCED\
\uc0\u9492 \u9472  Carry sentence (echoes point)  \u8592  ENHANCED\
\
Result: Chapter point appears 3 times in different forms
\f0 \
\
### Key Design Principles\
\
1. **Seed is implicit** (never states the skill/solution directly)\
2. **Experience is somatic** (body learns through exercise)\
3. **Name is explicit** (states point clearly post-exercise)\
4. **Punctuation creates emphasis** (no SSML pauses)\
5. **No verbatim repetition** (same point, different angles)\
\
